82
00:05:35,892 --> 00:05:39,255
To expose the player to some of the worst horrors of humanity,

83
00:05:39,255 --> 00:05:45,200
to tear them apart with a set of emotions that cause PTSD and an increased chance of suicide?

84
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:49,423
