00:11:55,697 --> 00:12:00,123
frolicking. The game shortcuts that experience to give the player the representation,

171
00:12:00,123 --> 00:12:03,768
and with it comes the risk that we eject them out of that experience.

172
00:12:04,638 --> 00:12:06,199
Is that what happens?

173
00:12:06,199 --> 00:12:08,161
Well, anyone who's been stuck on a table

