180
00:12:21,735 --> 00:12:24,618
We have to be aware of the change and build around it

181
00:12:24,618 --> 00:12:27,441
and take it into account, but we can still create emotion.

182
00:12:28,265 --> 00:12:32,968
Abstraction, though, is where the emotion is represented only as a concept.

183
00:12:32,968 --> 00:12:35,910
We don't expect an emotional response from the player here.

184
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:39,212
A good example of that would be player stats.

185
00:12:39,212 --> 00:12:43,315
When a stat changes, there's not an expectation that the player will then suddenly feel an

