189
00:12:54,823 --> 00:12:59,865
Okay, so simulation, representation and abstraction can help you bridge the divide between

190
00:12:59,865 --> 00:13:05,387
between emergence and authored narrative. It defines how you're aligning the content in the

191
00:13:05,387 --> 00:13:10,349
game and the player's emotional response to it. Please note too that this isn't a set of three

192
00:13:10,349 --> 00:13:16,071
distinct options, it's a spectrum. Each decision we make about our game can move the player closer

193
00:13:16,071 --> 00:13:21,153
to simulation or to abstraction, so we can fine-tune the player's relationship with the

194
00:13:21,153 --> 00:13:22,253
game and emotions as we go.

